divs: sighting detailsabout 9:19pm while driving to work i notice 4 or 5 bright yellow\organge orbs in the sky. i pulled over to see if i could get a photo. but they flickered out before i could. i then perceded on my way spotting only a few of them closer to town. again flickering out quickly. only a mile or so to work i looked up again and notice this time about 5 star like light blinking really rapidly. they were not in a specific formation or as best i could tell. i was so amped up at the sighting that i tried to call my friend. though it took about 5 minutes to get through since it kept saying no network. which is strange since i always get a signal. finally, i got through to my friend and told her. though while telling her it hurt my head. then faded back to normal. later that night i went on break and had another strange sighting this time it was a blue orb that shot across the sky. it looked similar to a shooting star only it was huge. i only wish that the people i was on break seen it to. needless to say it was an eventfull night.
Summary: Multiple UFO sightings on way to work.
